{"tid":2427883,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"工信部：今年要有序推進5G網絡建設 加快6G布局","createTime":"2021-03-01T06:27:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T11:32:31.000Z","uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b4d0a9a27b2f2fd89dbbc7c20c69f9af9a049239","tid":2427883,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T06:27:20.000Z","msg":"工信部新聞發言人田玉龍表示，大力推動信息通訊業的高質量發展，今年要有序推進5G網絡建設，加快6G的佈局，推動網絡優化的升級，確保網絡安全。<br />\n<br />\n工信部部長肖亞慶表示，新能源汽車的發展還處於爬坡過坎的關鍵時期。下一步要提高質量，進一步提高標準，進一步加強質量的監管，企業也要不斷提高製造水平。要促進融合，新能源汽車的發展還要有智慧道路、通信網絡、雲端技術等的集成，要通過電動化和智能網聯進一步融合，開拓出更好滿足消費者需要的新的功能。要優化環境，健全充電、停車等環保各項的措施，同時提高公共交通電動化的水平，擴大開放。"},{"pid":"bcf34dde502e85db25fdb7d1889fcd14b837b0fa","tid":2427883,"uid":104371,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T06:40:14.000Z","msg":"有冇人翻譯下"},{"pid":"f810d43cde77a932150d800941e030bfd8eb5140","tid":2427883,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcf34dde502e85db25fdb7d1889fcd14b837b0fa","tid":2427883,"uid":104371,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T06:40:14.000Z","msg":"有冇人翻譯下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T06:50:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ed740070c68fd4038a26a4b432a1a2aad9b20b","tid":2427883,"uid":288913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T06:51:44.000Z","msg":"即係5G obsolete左？"},{"pid":"c46b35dc22385e398c840271ddbeb9a3fd91fc0a","tid":2427883,"uid":36724,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bcf34dde502e85db25fdb7d1889fcd14b837b0fa","tid":2427883,"uid":104371,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T06:40:14.000Z","msg":"有冇人翻譯下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T06:51:55.000Z","msg":"紅色為重點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0